                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18360201-500-offence-1 t18360201-cd-85"></join>23rd of January</rs> 1 half-crown, the money of <persName id="t18360201-name-690" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-690" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-690" type="surname" value="SEARS"></interp>
